name: Pink Fog. 8x10 photograph
description:
This is a print from an instant Polaroid photograph taken in the beautiful forest of the rural Appalachian region of Virginia. This print has the characteristic soft focus of its original Polaroid photograph. The color has not been digitally enhanced.
 
Image size, approx. 8 1/4 x 10 1/4in.; 21 x 26cm
Printed on 8x10 in. glossy premium paper
Signed and dated on front border

This print is available on 4 x 6, 5 x 7, or 8 x 10 in. paper. Please feel free to contact me with any questions.

It's nice to have a little bit of outside inside.

name: Forest Vines. Photo on Maple wood block
description:
Three sides of this block are faced with a beautiful print made from a Polaroid photograph taken in the Appalachian forest of Virginia mounted on maple wood block. The smooth but unfinished wood block pairs nicely with the almost panoramic view of trees.

This block works as an object on a shelf or desk, and a small hole on the back allows for hanging on the wall.

The Polaroid process produces an image with soft focus and an intimate size, which invites close viewing. None of my prints have been digitally manipulated except to size them and correct colors to the original image.

Item will be shipped within 7 days in protective packaging.

It's nice to have a little bit of outside inside.
